nodes.text: CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 14:10:05 Edition was an in-universe CIS Shadowfeed issue published in Star Wars Insider 71.

This article was mistakenly printed with the incorrect in-universe date of 14:9:15, which corresponded with the date of the previous article released in Star Wars Insider 70, CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 14:9:15.
